asset.hookText:
Trying to get out on the streets in February in England can be a hard task. some days, it just won't happen and to get a skate you need to go undercover.
Volcom UK rider, Harry Lintell spent a couple of hours at Bay Sixty6 working on some tricks new and old.
Enjoy.
